41    """
42    SQLModel for the `app_suppression` table.
43
44    This model represents app suppression records in the billing system,
45    containing information about suppressed billing for specific apps.
46    """
47
48    id: int | None = Field(default=None, primary_key=True, description="Primary key, auto-incrementing")

61    modified_time: datetime.datetime = Field(description="Timestamp when the record was last modified")
62    finalization_time: datetime.datetime | None = Field(
63        default=None, description="Time when the suppression was finalized"
64    )
